com.google.inject.tools.suite.code
Class CodeRunner.Runnable

java.lang.Object
  com.google.inject.tools.suite.code.CodeRunner.Runnable
Enclosing interface:
CodeRunner
public abstract static class CodeRunner.Runnable
extends java.lang.Object

A Runnable is something the CodeRunner can run. It must implement the static main(String[] args) method and create a result that extends CodeSnippetResult which should be written to System.out as an object.
